  ExpressionUUID->"68d46c75-4124-4f94-b528-b4742dbd99a6"],
 "\[LineSeparator]identifies a knot by looking up the diagram in a table of \
named knots."
}], "Usage",ExpressionUUID->"add0985b-fd76-4bbe-8b74-dd4a062264b8"],

Cell["\<\
Returns an Association from each identified knot summand (a KnotSymbol[...]) \
to its multiplicity in the connect-sum decomposition. An unknot gives <||>. \
KnoodleIdentify only identifies knots; a genuine link (more than one \
component) fails with a message. input accepts the same representations as \
KnoodleDraw.\
\>", "Notes",ExpressionUUID->"8b0ac0c7-e7b8-4cec-a875-49419f454c9a"]
}, Open  ]],

